{"tid":587632,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜政府你贏左啦，大家都已經不再抱有希望啦","createTime":"2018-03-10T14:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T14:33:09.000Z","uid":90290,"like":13,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0e2e09110eedab9add9aeab8cb8204342089cb","tid":587632,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"話說聽日補選，今日同班朋友食飯，竟然冇講呢個話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年大家都有去雨革，我諗住大家既抱負到今日仲係一樣，但睇到佢地咁既態度，我就知道可能得返我一個仲幻想香港係有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺我講起「大家聽日記得投票」先嘅<br />\n大家嘅答覆都係 冇個鐘意、個個都on9<br />\n我話:萬一俾建制入咗，一定立法23條，乜法都批㗎！就算泛民做唔到實事，投到個反對票都好啦！<br />\n結果大家都係話，算啦，唔投啦，冇個想投<br />\n<br />\n喺嗰刻我先發現自己其實好天真.....原來大家都已經肯定咗香港係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6679fba620c0982e112075cc36706fa187153a9e","tid":587632,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"大家記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2915bf0852ccb5d21cfcdbfa1604024a0fd8af86","tid":587632,"uid":2210,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"不分黨派，票投民主"},{"pid":"10e7ad302bf24ec9b2a44165e62cf5581668079e","tid":587632,"uid":146621,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"支持建制搞彎香港<br />\n等廢老知道冇人&quot;搞事&quot;<br />\n香港會變成點"},{"pid":"c7a6da24ec839668b4bd3e7432b0a1e767d5612f","tid":587632,"uid":39221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10e7ad302bf24ec9b2a44165e62cf5581668079e","tid":587632,"uid":146621,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"支持建制搞彎香港<br />\n等廢老知道冇人&quot;搞事&quot;<br />\n香港會變成點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:38:19.000Z","